Blaze.uk.description: Extraordinary Engineering: An argument for the Ancient Astronaut theory is the engineering evident in the construction of ancient megalithic sites worldwide. (S1, ep 1)

Blaze.uk.title: The UnXplained: of the Universe
Blaze.uk.description: Venus: Earth's Evil Twin: Earth's neighbour has volcanoes, clouds of acid rain and a surface temperature hot enough to melt lead - so is Venus our evil twin? (S1, ep 4)

Blaze.uk.title: Storage Wars Texas
Blaze.uk.description: Spurs Of The Moment: The auction returns to the small Texas town of Ponder, where Ricky and Bubba look to extend a lucky streak, as Jenny discovers her inner ballerina. (S6, ep 2)

Blaze.uk.title: Storage Wars Texas
Blaze.uk.description: Float Like A Bubbafly: The auction action moves to Dallas. After Kenny Stowe flashes his fat wallet, Bubba takes him on in a bidding battle to remember. (S6, ep 4)

Blaze.uk.title: Storage Wars Texas
Blaze.uk.description: Grounded & Pounded: In Plano, a locker of mixed martial arts gear puts Kenny in a compromising position. Meanwhile, Mary shows her ambition and Jenny dares to get devious. (S6, ep 6)

Blaze.uk.title: Storage Wars Texas
Blaze.uk.description: Fear The Short Fat Man: The bidders head to auctions in the small town of Waxahachie, where Jenny makes a scandalous discovery that could give her the payday of a lifetime. (S6, ep 8)

Blaze.uk.title: Storage Wars Texas
Blaze.uk.description: Welcome To The World Of The Sonny Monday: The buyers come up against a determined bunch of locals at auctions in Waxahachie. Can they beat them to the lockers' treasures? (S6, ep 10)

Blaze.uk.title: Container Wars
Blaze.uk.description: The Big Apple: Containers from New York make their way to Long Beach, California, bidders are interested in a billionaire's unclaimed goods and a one-of-a-kind auction is held. (S2, ep 3)

Blaze.uk.title: Container Wars
Blaze.uk.description: Sailing Away: The Israelis go after what they think is vintage clothing. Meanwhile, a custom container could land a buyer in jail. (S2, ep 5)

Blaze.uk.title: Container Wars
Blaze.uk.description: Surf's Up: A surprise item may send the Israelis in search of major dollars. Jason strikes on a container full of wood and weird gear. (S2, ep 7)

Blaze.uk.title: Container Wars
Blaze.uk.description: New Blood: A new team surface and pose a threat to Mo, a three-wheeled item entices Matthew and a cluster of table-tennis balls cause confusion. (S2, ep 9)

Blaze.uk.title: Container Wars
Blaze.uk.description: Outdoor Adventure: Buyers clash over a playground, a treasure trove of bicycle gear and a mystery container. (S2, ep 11)

Blaze.uk.title: History's Greatest Mysteries
Blaze.uk.description: The 'Missingest' Man in America: Explore the theories behind the disappearance of former New York Supreme Court judge Joseph Force Crater in 1930, a case which remains unsolved. (S4, ep 7)

Blaze.uk.title: The Curse Of Oak Island
Blaze.uk.description: A Void at All Costs: As the team experiences a disappointing setback, they're stunned to learn it may have led to a breakthrough discovery. (S11, ep 8)

Blaze.uk.title: New: The Great British Dig
Blaze.uk.description: Lenton, Nottingham: Hugh and the team unearth William the Conqueror's lost priory hidden beneath Lenton in Nottingham. (S1, ep 3)

Blaze.uk.title: New: Greatest Prison Escapes...
Blaze.uk.description: Time and a Half: Correctional officer Kay Beeman feigns being a hostage to facilitate her inmate boyfriend's escape. Their recapture would take months. (S1, ep 8)

Blaze.uk.title: Ancient Murders Unearthed
Blaze.uk.description: Rosemarkie Man: Homicide detective Rod Demery and forensic scientist Turi King examine a murder victim dated to the time of the Picts, unearthed in a remote sea cave in Scotland. (S1, ep 1)

UAndWPlus1.uk.title: Inside the Ambulance
UAndWPlus1.uk.description: Adam and Jenine try to help a woman who's fallen from a first-floor window, while Laura and Natalie deal with a former paramedic who appears to have had a stroke. S7 Ep1

UAndWPlus1.uk.title: Inside the Ambulance
